
This directory contains the implementation of
a program that demostrates the algorithm prsented in
"Gridless Controllable Fire"

To Make and execute program:

1) Set SDKROOT in the Makefile to the root directory where
the SDK (directory structure of SDK is assumed to be
as in nVidia) for the graphics card is installed.

2) make

3) execute  by typing

./GLFireDemo

on command line

typing 'h' key when the program is running gives a
help on the possible actions.
